movie.title: Tanu Weds Manu Returns
movie.description_intro: Tanu and Manu's marriage collapses. What happens when Manu meets Tanu's lookalike Kusum - and when Tanu returns?

movies.title: Blackbeard's Ghost
movies.summary: In this comedy, Sir Peter Ustinov is the famous pirate's ghost that returns to our time. Blackbeard has been cursed by his last wife who was a notorious witch, so that he will never die. The only way to "break" the curse is to do (for once in his life) a good act. Is the famous pirate able to do something good?

movies.summary: A disparate variety of couples from all walks of life strive to maintain active sex lives despite the notable distraction of having kids.

movies.title: Let's Kill Ward's Wife
movies.summary: Ward's wife is a bitch. Everyone knows it. Including Ward. After numerous conversations and ruminations on the subject amongst Ward's colorful group of friends, a fortuitous accident leads to a whole new world of problems and possibilities.

movies.title: Love Over Distance
movies.summary: Successful Evi loves her busy life in Rotterdam. She lives in an apartment to die for with her boyfriend Len and works really hard as an engineer. She is called in to see her boss: she is being relocated. She can't wait to hear her dream come true. But then, to her complete dismay, she hears that she is being relocated not to Rio de Janeiro, but to - Terneuzen, a small town in the south of the Netherlands.
